OL,3,CSexual harassment and sexism rife in
OL,4,Cschools, report finds
OL,6,FSexual harassment and sexism is "rife"
OL,7,Fin schools, with support staff
OL,8,Fcomplaining of physical advances and
OL,9,Flewd remarks, according to a new
OL,10,Freport.
OL,12,FUnison said its study showed that one
OL,13,Fin 10 female support staff in
OL,14,Fsecondary schools revealed they have
OL,15,Fbeen sexually harassed, mainly by male
OL,16,Fpupils but also by male colleagues.
