OL,3,CSexual harassment and sexism rife in
OL,4,Cschools, report finds
OL,6,FResponses from more than 2,000
OL,7,Femployees across the UK working mostly
OL,8,Fin primary and secondary education,
OL,9,Fincluded teaching assistants,
OL,10,Ftechnicians, lunchtime supervisors and
OL,11,Fadministrators, showed a number of
OL,12,Fincidents.
OL,14,FThese included a male student trying
OL,15,Fto kiss a female worker and pushing
OL,16,Fher head into his crotch, boys trying
OL,17,Fto touch or slap a staff member's
OL,18,Fbottom and a headteacher telling a
OL,19,Ffemale colleague to "stand here and
OL,20,Flook pretty, I'll do the talking".
