OL,3,CSexual harassment and sexism rife in
OL,4,Cschools, report finds
OL,6,FUnison general secretary Christina
OL,7,FMcAnea said: "Parents will be
OL,8,Fhorrified to learn their children are
OL,9,Fbeing taught in such toxic
OL,10,Fenvironments. The danger is that
OL,11,Flanguage and behaviour learned at an
OL,12,Fearly age stay with pupils as they
OL,13,Fbecome adults and go out into the
OL,14,Fwider world.
OL,16,F"Any male staff with such outdated
OL,17,Fattitudes need to think carefully
OL,18,Fabout how they interact with
OL,19,Fcolleagues and pupils. They must ditch
OL,20,Fsuch highly inappropriate behaviour
OL,21,Fimmediately.
