OL,3,CSexual harassment and sexism rife in
OL,4,Cschools, report finds
OL,6,F"But clearly, schools can't tackle
OL,7,Fthis huge problem on their own.
OL,8,FParents have a proper role to play
OL,9,Ftoo. Sexist and demeaning words have
OL,10,Fno place in the modern class or staff
OL,11,Froom.
OL,13,F"The role of misogynist influencers
OL,14,Fcannot be overstated. A solution must
OL,15,Fbe found before this worrying issue
OL,16,Fspirals out of control."
