OL,3,CSexual harassment and sexism rife in
OL,4,Cschools, report finds
OL,6,FNina Humphries of Feminista, which
OL,7,Fhelped with the report, added: "It is
OL,8,Fdeeply concerning that misogyny is so
OL,9,Fnormalised in schools. This fuels
OL,10,Fviolence against women and girls and
OL,11,Flimits the aspirations of all young
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,F"These joint survey results contribute
OL,15,Fto the abundance of evidence that
OL,16,Fsexism and sexual harassment are rife
OL,17,Fin the UK education system. Staff and
OL,18,Fstudents alike face this unacceptable
OL,19,Fbehaviour. More must be done to make
OL,20,Fschools and colleges safer."
